LaTeX/LyX 2.0:
	No installation is necessary, simply work in the same folder
	as the style files (*.sty).
LyX 1.x (Linux, Mac OS X):
	1) Run "install-lyx.sh" (./install-lyx.sh in a terminal)
	2) Run LyX and select "Reconfigure" from the "Tools" menu.
	3) Restart lyx
	4) Load the example thesis
LyX 1.x (Windows):
	1) Run "install-lyx.bat"
	2) Run LyX and select "Reconfigure" from the "Tools" menu.
	3) Restart lyx
	4) Load the example thesis
